3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20former%20PepsiCo%20exec%20sued%20the%20company%20for%20fraud%20and%20defamation%20after%20it%20said%20he%20didn't%20invent%20Flamin'%20Hot%20Cheetos.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERichard%20Monta%C3%B1ez%20said%20he%20proposed%20the%20idea%20while%20working%20as%20a%20janitor%20and%20ultimately%20rose%20through%20the%20company's%20ranks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20PepsiCo%20told%20The%20LA%20Times%20in%202021%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20facts%20do%20not%20support%20the%20urban%20legend.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20former%20executive%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpepsico-pepsi-high-prices-putting-off-us-shoppers-sales-america-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPepsiCo%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20sued%20the%20company%2C%20claiming%20he%20should%20get%20credit%20for%20being%20the%20brains%20behind%20Flamin'%20Hot%20Cheetos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERichard%20Monta%C3%B1ez%20has%20frequently%20spoken%20of%20his%20rags-to-riches%20story%2C%20from%20starting%20out%20as%20a%20janitor%20to%20pitching%20the%20idea%20for%20Flamin'%20Hot%20Cheetos%20to%20PepsiCo's%20CEO%20to%20becoming%20an%20executive%20himself%20at%20the%20drink%20and%20snack%20giant%2C%20which%20formed%20the%20basis%20of%20his%20successful%20career%20as%20a%20motivational%20speaker.%20He%20published%20a%20memoir%20in%202021%2C%20and%20his%20life%20story%20was%20made%20into%20the%20film%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflamin-hot-cheetos-movie-devon-franklin-eva-longoria-richard-montanez-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BFlamin'%20Hot%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20an%20explosive%20Los%20Angeles%20Times%20investigation%20in%202021%20claimed%20to%20debunk%20his%20claims%20about%20the%20origins%20of%20the%20Flamin'%20Hot%20flavor%2C%20supported%20by%20evidence%20from%20PepsiCo.%20Monta%C3%B1ez%20filed%20a%20six-count%20lawsuit%20against%20his%20former%20employer%20on%20July%2018%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20fraud%20and%20defamation%20for%20making%20the%20comments%20to%20the%20publication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPepsiCo%20declined%20to%20comment%20when%20contacted%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20citing%20ongoing%20litigation.%20Frito-Lay%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2250d637c8-24bb-4f4b-b71e-955486143747%5C%22%3EMonta%C3%B1ez%20says%20he%20pitched%20spicy%20Cheetos%20while%20working%20as%20a%20janitor%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERichard%20Monta%C3%B1ez's%20PepsiCo%20career%20began%20in%201976%20when%20he%20started%20working%20as%20a%20janitor%20at%20its%20Frito-Lay%20factory%20in%20Rancho%20Cucamonga%2C%20California%2C%20per%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20time%20at%20the%20company%2C%20he%20experimented%20with%20making%20various%20flavored%20snacks%20at%20home%20to%20potentially%20pitch%20to%20the%20company%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%20But%20his%20big%20breakthrough%20came%20when%20a%20machine%20in%20the%20factory%20broke%2C%20and%20he%20was%20able%20to%20take%20home%20a%20batch%20of%20unflavored%20Cheetos%2C%20which%20he%20dusted%20with%20chile%20powder%20to%20try%20to%20replicate%20the%20flavor%20of%20elote%2C%20Mexican%20grilled%20corn%20with%20chile%20powder%2C%20per%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201991%2C%20Monta%C3%B1ez%20set%20up%20a%20meeting%20with%20PepsiCo%20CEO%20Roger%20Enrico%20to%20present%20his%20idea%20for%20spicy%20Cheetos%2C%20which%20he%20thought%20would%20be%20popular%20with%20the%20Latino%20community.%20Enrico%20liked%20the%20idea%20so%20much%20that%20he%20ordered%20PepsiCo%20to%20start%20making%20spicy%20Cheetos%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20PepsiCo%20%26quot%3Battempted%20to%20cut%20Mr.%20Monta%C3%B1ez%20out%20of%20parts%20of%20the%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPepsiCo%20launched%20nationwide%20sales%20of%20Flamin'%20Hot%20Cheetos%20in%201992.%20The%20product%20has%20since%20become%20a%20huge%20success%20for%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPepsiCo%20sent%20Monta%C3%B1ez%20on%20speaking%20engagements%20at%20places%20including%20Walmart%2C%20Target%2C%20and%20Harvard%20University%20to%20talk%20about%20how%20he%20developed%20the%20product%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMonta%C3%B1ez%20continued%20to%20develop%20other%20spicy%20snacks%20for%20PepsiCo%20and%20ultimately%20became%20PepsiCo's%20vice%20president%20of%20multicultural%20marketing%20and%20sales%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMonta%C3%B1ez%20left%20PepsiCo%20in%202019%20to%20dedicate%20his%20time%20to%20motivational%20speaking%2C%20charging%20between%20%2410%2C000%20and%20%2450%2C000%20per%20talk%2C%20per%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228aaa9bfb-7665-40b0-802a-bb8d71ca3b4f%5C%22%3EFrito-Lay%20says%20the%20'facts%20do%20not%20support%20the%20urban%20legend'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMonta%C3%B1ez's%20story%20has%20been%20disputed.%20In%202021%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Fstory%2F2021-05-16%2Fflamin-hot-cheetos-richard-montanez%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Los%20Angeles%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20an%20investigation%20that%20seemed%20to%20debunk%20Monta%C3%B1ez's%20claims.%20More%20than%20a%20dozen%20former%20Frito-Lay%20employees%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20company%20itself%2C%20told%20the%20outlet%20that%20Monta%C3%B1ez%20wasn't%20behind%20the%20development%20of%20the%20Flamin'%20Hot%20flavor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20credit%20the%20creation%20of%20Flamin'%20Hot%20Cheetos%20or%20any%20Flamin'%20Hot%20products%20to%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Frito-Lay%20told%20The%20Times%2C%20adding%20that%20its%20records%20didn't%20show%20that%20he%20was%20involved%20%26quot%3Bin%20any%20capacity%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20product's%20test%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20facts%20do%20not%20support%20the%20urban%20legend%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn