20success%20of%20Flamin'%20Hot%20Cheetos%20%26quot%3Band%20other%20products%26quot%3B%20to%20several%20people%2C%20including%20Monta%C3%B1ez.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMonta%C3%B1ez%20%26quot%3Bhad%20a%20remarkable%2040-plus-year%20career%20at%20PepsiCo%20and%20made%20an%20incredible%20impact%20on%20our%20business%20and%20employees%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%20PepsiCo's%20previous%20comments%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bmisconstrued%26quot%3B%20and%20fractured%20its%20relationship%20with%20Monta%C3%B1ez%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20accused%20PepsiCo%20of%20fraud%20and%20defamation%20and%20said%20the%20company%20discriminated%20against%20Monta%C3%B1ez%20because%20he%20was%20Mexican.%20It%20is%20seeking%20damages%20and%20an%20order%20preventing%20the%20company%20from%20making%20comments%20suggesting%20Monta%C3%B1ez%20didn't%20create%20the%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflamin-hot-cheetos-richard-montanez-sues-company-development-creation-pepsico2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722330083000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a77abea0fc5856d5981a00%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflamin-hot-cheetos-richard-montanez-sues-company-development-creation-pepsico2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Richard%20Monta%C3%B1ez%20claimed%20to%20have%20invented%20the%20snack%20after%20putting%20chile%20powder%20on%20a%20batch%20of%20plain%20Cheetos%20in%20his%20home.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22gdean%40businessinsider.com%20(Grace%20Dean)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflamin-hot-cheetos-richard-montanez-sues-company-development-creation-pepsico2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22AI%20risks%20destroying%20jobs.%20Tech%20leaders%20think%20they%2