%2C%20which%20are%20crucial%20for%20sustaining%20good%20posture%20throughout%20daily%20activities%2C%20Dawance%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20traditional%20Pilates%20workouts%20aren't%20quite%20the%20same%20as%20clinical%20Pilates%20workouts%20offered%20by%20physiotherapists%20or%20other%20trained%20healthcare%20professionals%2C%20Elizabeth%20Lee%2C%20a%20physiotherapist%20specializing%20in%20spinal%20care%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.therehablabsg.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Rehab%20Lab%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20sports%20and%20spine%20physiotherapy%20clinic%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20traditional%20Pilates%20can%20be%20beneficial%20for%20general%20fitness%20and%20mild%20postural%20issues%2C%20clinical%20Pilates%20offers%20a%20more%20specialized%20approach%20for%20those%20with%20specific%20spinal%20concerns%20or%20persistent%20low%20back%20pain%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20both%20forms%20of%20Pilates%20can%20help%20strengthen%20core%20muscles%20that%20support%20the%20spine%20as%20well%20as%20promote%20balanced%20muscle%20development%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20it's%20crucial%20to%20understand%20that%20posture%20has%20both%20static%20and%20dynamic%20components.%20Our%20body%20needs%20to%20cope%20with%20the%20demands%20of%20various%20activities%20like%20walking%2C%20running%2C%20jumping%2C%20throwing%2C%20and%20lifting%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20standing%20or%20sitting%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20said.%20%26quot%3BClinical%20Pilates%20addresses%20this%20by%20incorporating%20functional%20movements%20that%20translate%20to%20daily%20activities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPilates%20aside%2C%20there%20are%20other%20simpler%20exercises%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20neck%20presses%20and%20chest%20stretches%20%E2%80%94%20that%20can%20also%20help%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Ffitness%2Fhow-to-fix-posture%5C%22%20target%3D%