sruptions-start-to-ease%3Fsrnd%3Dhomepage-americas%26sref%3Dh4tCfJuJ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereputational%20damages%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-customers-refund-crowdstrike-outage-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eticket%20refunds%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3EBloomberg%20reported%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222a7bbac6-465f-4ddb-825d-9b3c2f5f5106%5C%22%3ELiability%20limited%20to%20refunds%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Delta%20and%20its%20new%20team%20of%20Boies-led%20lawyers%20might%20not%20be%20able%20to%20get%20much%20from%20CrowdStrike%2C%20experts%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cybersecurity%20firm's%20terms%20and%20conditions%20say%20that%20CrowdStrike%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrowdstrike-terms-conditions-limits-damages-to-refund-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edoesn't%20have%20to%20shell%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20anything%20more%20than%20a%20refund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.crowdstrike.com%2Fterms-conditions%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eterms%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20CrowdStrike's%20Falcon%20security%20software%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmass-it-outage-companies-operations-airlines-affected-microsoft-crowdstrike-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eused%20by%20companies%20and%20government%20agencies%20around%20the%20world%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20limit%20liability%20to%20%26quot%3Bfees%20paid.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20that%20if%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecompanies%20like%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDelta%20had%20a%20claim%20for%20damage%20or%20lost%20revenue%2C%20CrowdStrike%20would%20only%20pay%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethose%20companies%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20cost%20of%20the%20software%2C%20Elizabeth%20Burgin%20Waller%2C%20the%20chair%20of%20the%20Cybersecurity%20%26amp%3B%20Data%20Privacy%20practice%20at%20Woods%20Rogers%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrowdstrike-terms-conditions-limits-damages-to-refund-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Business%20Insider%20%3C%2Fa%3Eearlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDelta%20would%20have%20to%20overcome%20the%20harsh%20limitation%20of%20liability%20provisions%20that%20CrowdStrike%20drafted%20into%20its%20contract%20with%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20Haim%20Ravia%20and%20Dotan%20Hammer%2C%20cyber%20and%20privacy%20partners%20at%20law%20firm%20Pearl%20Cohen%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20note%20to%20Business%20Insider.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20any%20negligence%20claims%2C%20%26quot%3BDelta%20would%20need%20to%20prove%20that%20its%20harm%20was%20reasonably%20anticipated%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawyers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20individuals%20hoping%20to%20seek%20damages%20from%20CrowdStrike%20through%20proposed%20class%20action%20lawsuits%20may%20have%20little%20luck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20class%20action%20against%20CrowdStrike%20would%20face%20challenges%20demonstrating%20whether%20the%20harm%20suffered%20is%20similar%20throughout%20the%20entire%20class%2C%20the%20partners%20at%20Pearl%20Cohen%20said.%20This%20means%20that%20individual%20victims%2C%20small%20companies%2C%20and%20large%20companies%20cannot%20group%20together%20against%20CrowdStrike%2C%20since%20the%20harm%20to%20them%20is%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMauricio%20Sanchez%2C%C2%A0a%20senior%20director%20at%20a%20tech%20market%20research%20firm%20Dell'Oro%20Group%2C%20said%20that%20CrowdStrike%20may%20not%20have%20to%20pay%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20it%20will%20be%20a%20miserable%20summer%20for%20CrowdStrike%20lawyers%2C%20as%20they%20defend%20themselves%20from%20customers%20with%20torches%20and%20pitchforks%2C%20I%20don't%20see%20CrowdStrike%20having%20to%20pay%20much%2C%20if%20any%2C%20compensation%2C%26quot%3B%20Sanchez%20told%20trade%20publication%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fierce-network.com%2Fcloud%2Fcrowdstrike-has-target-its-back-after-outage%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFierce%20Network%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20case%20%E2%80%94%20this%20one%20about%20hacking%2C%20not%20just%20a%20software%20update%20gone%20wrong%20%E2%80%94%20offers%20some%20precedent%20for%20how%20big%20customers%20like%20Delta%20could%20fare%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsolarwinds-hack-explained-government-agencies-cyber-security-2020-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehackers%20broke%20into%20Texas-based%20SolarWinds'%3C%2Fa%3E%20systems%20and%20added%20malicious%20code%20to%20the%20company's%20software%20system.%20More%20than%2030%2C000%20customers%20then%20were%20unwittingly%20sent%20software%20updates%20that%20included%20the%20hacked%20code%2C%20which%20led%20to%20hackers%20spying%20on%20company%20and%20government%20organizations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20a%20US%20judge%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Flegal%2Fus-judge-dismisses-most-sec-lawsuit-against-solarwinds-concerning-cyberattack-2024-07-18%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520SEC%2520alleged%2520that%2520SolarWinds%2Cabout%2520malicious%2520activity%2520involving%2520Orion.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edismissed%3C%2Fa%3E%20most%20of%20a%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%20lawsuit%20accusing%20SolarWinds%20of%20defrauding%20investors%20by%20hiding%20security%20weaknesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20customer%20agreements%20that%20favor%20CrowdStrike%20and%20SolarWinds%20largely%20beating%20the%20SEC%2C%20CrowdStrike%20stands%20a%20good%20chance%20in%20court%2C%20Sanchez%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Selbst%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20at%20UCLA%20School%20of%20Law%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhls.harvard.edu%2Ftoday%2Fharvard-law-expert-discusses-data-breaches-failures-and-the-vulnerability-of-everyday-technology%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHarvard%20Law%20Today%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20week%20that%20customers%20could%20sue%20over%20negligence%2C%20a%20common%20class%20action%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUltimately%2C%20they're%20difficult%20to%20win%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20consequence%20for%20CrowdStrike%20could%20be%20regulation%2C%20especially%20from%20the%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20FTC%20has%20a%20pattern%20of%20settling%20with%20these%20companies%20and%20keeping%20them%20under%20a%20consent%20decree%20for%2020%20years%20or%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20Selbst%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20with%20the%20FTC%2C%20you%20don't%20get%20individual%20customers%20receiving%20damages%20or%20compensation.%20This%20is%20just%20a%20regulatory%20regime%2C%20and%20they%20receive%20fines%20payable%20to%20the%20federal%20government.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-hires-david-boies-lawyers-crowdstrike-microsoft-pay-damages-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722326417000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e806d1a7adf700190795d4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-hires-david-boies-lawyers-crowdstrike-microsoft-pay-damages-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20carrier%20has%20hired%20star%20attorney%20David%20Boies%20to%20seek%20damages%20from%20CrowdStrike%20and%20Microsoft%20for%20the%20computer%20outage%2C%20CNBC%20reported.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22shubhangigoel%40insider.com%20(Shubhangi%20Goel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-hires-david-boies-lawyers-crowdstrike-microsoft-pay-damages-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Yogi%20Adityanath%20Takes%20Dig%20At%20Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20Uncle%2C%20Gets%20A%20%26quot%3BDeputy%26quot%3B%20Reply%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath's%20swipe%20at%20Samajwadi%20Party%20leader%20and%20Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20uncle%20Shivpal%20Yadav%20drew%20a%20sharp%20counter%20in%20the%20Assembly%20this%20morning.%C2%A0At%20the%20beginning%20of%20his%20address%20in%20the%20House%2C%20Mr%20Adityanath%20congratulated%20Samajwadi%20Party%20veteran%20Mata%20Prasad%20Pandey%2C%20who%20has%20replaced%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20as%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20after%20the%20party%20chief%20was%20elected%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20from%20Kannauj%20in%20this%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20Mr%20Pandey%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20served%20twice%20as%20the%20Speaker%20of%20this%20House.%20I%20congratulate%20you%20on%20your%20selection.%20It's%20a%20different%20matter%20that%20you%20tricked%20chacha%20(uncle).%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Adityanath%20was%20referring%20to%20Shivpal%20Singh%20Yadav%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20uncle%2C%20who%20was%20seated%20next%20to%20Mr%20Pandey.%C2%A0%26quot%3BChacha%20always%20gets%20tricked%20like%20this.%20This%20is%20his%20destiny%20because%20the%20nephew%20is%20always%20scared%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Shivpal%20Yadav%20was%20seen%20smiling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20veteran%20leader%20waited%20for%20his%20turn.%20When%20he%20rose%20to%20speak%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20not%20tricked%2C%20Pandey%20ji%20is%20very%20senior.%26quot%3B%20Addressing%20the%20treasury%20benches%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20in%20touch%20with%20you%20for%20three%20years.%20You%20tricked%20me%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20as%20MLAs%20cutting%20across%20party%20lines%2C%20including%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20burst%20into%20laughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShivpal%20Yadav%20then%20took%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20BJP's%20lack-lustre%20show%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20in%20this%20election.%20%26quot%3BYou%20tricked%20me%2C%20you%20lagged%20behind%20in%20this%20election%20and%20Samajwadi%20Party%20stormed%20ahead.%20Mark%20my%20words%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20will%20come%20to%20power%20in%20the%202027%20(state%20polls)%20and%20your%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20will%20trick%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seasoned%20leader's%20remarks%20came%20amid%20friction%20within%20the%20state%20BJP.%20In%20a%20show%20of%20united%20front%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20was%20flanked%20by%20Deputy%20Chief%20Ministers%20Maurya%20and%20Brajesh%20Pathak%20when%20he%20addressed%20the%20media%20before%20the%20Assembly%20session%20began%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20youngest%20brother%20of%20former%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20Samajwadi%20Party%20founder%2C%20the%20late%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%2C%20Shivpal%20Yadav%20has%20served%20as%20an%20MLA%20for%20nearly%20three%20decades%20now.%20He%20has%20also%20been%20a%20state%20minister%20and%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition.%20He%20is%20now%20the%20National%20General%20Secretary%20of%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%202017%2C%20when%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20was%20coming%20of%20age%20politically%20and%20taking%20charge%20of%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20Shivpal%20Yadav%20quit%20the%20party%20and%20founded%20the%20Pragatisheel%20Samajwadi%20Party.%20In%202022%2C%20Shivpal%20Yadav%20cleared%20his%20differences%20with%20nephew%20Akhilesh%2C%20rejoined%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20merged%20his%20party%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722326100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F1mpo4bio_yogi-shivpal_625x300_30_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fyogi-adityanath-shivpal-yadav-akhilesh-yadav-yogi-adityanath-takes-dig-at-akhilesh-yadavs-uncle-gets-a-deputy-reply-6221279%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%