n%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20game%20was%20a%20tight%20affair%20with%20both%20players%20going%20neck%20and%20neck.%20At%208-8%2C%20Manika%20induced%20a%20backhand%20error%20from%20her%20young%20rival%20and%20closed%20the%20game%20with%20a%20ferocious%20forehand%20drive%20that%20Prithika%20could%20not%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManika%20carried%20the%20momentum%20in%20the%20second%20game%2C%20taking%20a%203-1%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrithika%20fought%20back%20to%20level%20the%20scores%2C%20inducing%20errors%20from%20the%20Indian.%20However%2C%20Manika's%20attack%20on%20Prithika's%20backhand%20got%20her%20points%20consistently.%20In%20no%20time%2C%20she%20was%20leading%209-6.%20Consecutive%20backhand%20errors%20from%20Prithika%20handed%20Manika%20the%20second%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20stopping%20the%20seasoned%20Indian%2C%20who%20got%20a%20healthy%203-0%20cushion%20in%20game%20three%20as%20Prithika%20struggled%20with%20her%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20desperate%20Prithika%20went%20all%20out%20and%20got%20her%20first%20point%20with%20a%20thumping%20forehand%20winner.%20With%20a%205-1%20lead%20in%20hand%2C%20Manika%20kept%20attacking%20the%20backhand%20side%20of%20the%20French%20player%2C%20making%20it%208-4.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrailing%205-10%2C%20Prithika%20made%20it%20a%20contest%20by%20taking%20four%20points%20in%20a%20row%20but%20Manika%20needed%20just%20one%20more%20to%20close%20the%20game.%20The%20home%20favourite%20netted%20a%20backhand%20drive%20to%20concede%20the%20game%20and%20a%203-0%20lead%20to%20the%20Indian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20ferocious%20forehand%20gave%20Manika%20a%2010-5%20lead%20in%20the%20fourth%20game%20and%20five%20match%20points.%20She%20converted%20the%20third%20when%20Prithika%20netted%20her%20backhand%20to%20win%20the%20match%20in%2037%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722320100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Flfrt8vqg_manika-batra-afp_625x300_30_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22origi