ed%20into%20question%20how%20effective%20the%20operation%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20USS%20Tarawa%20is%20an%20amphibious%20assault%20ship%20that%20served%20in%20the%20US%20from%201976%20to%202009%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20outlet%20said.%20%26quot%3BSuch%20an%20outdated%20ship%20cannot%20be%20compared%20with%20modern%20military%20equipment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20SINKEX%20operation%20comes%20as%20China's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-needs-naval-coalition-stand-up-to-china-retired-admiral-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enavy%20fleet%20grows%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20poses%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20South%20China%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20overtaken%20the%20US%20Navy%20in%20fleet%20size.%20%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Pentagon's%202023%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.defense.gov%2F2023%2FOct%2F19%2F2003323409%2F-1%2F-1%2F1%2F2023-MILITARY-AND-SECURITY-DEVELOPMENTS-INVOLVING-THE-PEOPLES-REPUBLIC-OF-CHINA.PDF%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EChina%20Military%20Power%20Report%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20its%20fleet%20has%20about%20370%20vessels.%20By%20contrast%2C%20the%20US%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsgp.fas.org%2Fcrs%2Fweapons%2FRL32665.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efleet%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20down%20to%20just%20under%20300%20ships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20the%20US%20Navy%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-showed-can-sink-820-ft-ship-china-not-impressed-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722317593000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a8517afb6d32635ee4c8e8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busin