12w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG_0730_11zon-1722256363-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG_0730_11zon-1722256363-500x667.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG_0730_11zon-1722256363-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG_0730_11zon-1722256363-1152x1536.jpg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG_0730_11zon-1722256363-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG_0730_11zon-1722256363-150x200.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358947%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERachna%20with%20one%20of%20her%20creations.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20is%20her%20shop%20the%20only%20one%20of%20its%20kind%20here%2C%20but%20what%20also%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emakes%20her%20stand%20out%20is%20her%20grit%20and%20courage.%20Every%20morning%2C%20even%20before%20her%20mother%20awakens%2C%20she%20finishes%20cooking%20and%20cleaning%20before%20cycling%205%20km%20from%20her%20house%20in%20Risia%20block%E2%80%99s%20Chhitan%20Purva%20village%20to%20run%20her%20shop%20alone.%20It%20is%20this%20indomitable%20spirit%20and%20determination%20that%20has%20helped%20Rachna%20follow%20her%20dreams.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20aspirational%20district%20with%20low%20socio-economic%20indicators%20where%20girls%20are%20married%20soon%20after%20reaching%20puberty%2C%20Rachna%20too%2C%20would%20have%20met%20the%20same%20fate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20to%20drop%20out%20of%20school%20due%20to%20family%E2%80%99s%20financial%20constraints%2C%20she%20resisted%20early%20marriage%20and%20dared%20to%20pursue%20her%20dreams%20to%20become%20an%20artist%20and%20an%20entrepreneur.%20Over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20she%20has%20sold%20about%20200%20of%20her%20paintings%2C%2050%20of%20which%20were%20bought%20since%20she%20opened%20her%20shop%20in%20April%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20she%20achieved%20this%20admirable%20feat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhen%20opportunities%20make%20dreams%20come%20true%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202019%2C%20Rachna%20had%20almost%20given%20up%20on%20life.%20%E2%80%9CI%20became%20depressed%20after%20dropping%20out.%20I%20thought%20I%20would%20have%20to%20spend%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20days%20doing%20household%20chores.%20As%20the%20eldest%20of%20five%20siblings%2C%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20on%20me%20to%20get%20married%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Rachna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20this%20time%2C%20the%20Aga%20Khan%20Foundation%20(AKF)%20came%20into%20the%20picture%20with%20Project%20Lehar.%20Started%20to%20provide%20vocational%20training%2C%20entrepreneurship%2C%20and%20life%20skills%20courses%20to%20marginalised%20young%20women%2C%20Project%20Lehar%2C%20run%20by%20AKF%20in%20partnership%20with%20The%20King%E2%80%99s%20Trust%20International%2C%20empowers%20girls%20and%20young%20women%20from%20disadvantaged%20backgrounds%20to%20rediscover%20and%20realise%20their%20potential.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Project%20Lehar%20team%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F290617%2Fsonal-shukla-educated-girls-mumbai-slums-feminist-icon-women-movement-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereaching%20out%20to%20help%20school%20dropouts%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Risia%20block%20restart%20their%20education.%20This%20was%20a%20godsend%20opportunity%20for%20Rachna%20to%20not%20just%20resume%20her%20studies%20but%20also%20to%20convince%20her%20parents%20to%20drop%20her%20marriage%20plans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20she%20was%20admitted%20into%20college%20through%20Project%20Lehar%2C%20she%20was%20also%20counseled%20on%20entrepreneurial%20and%20career%20prospects.%20One%20such%20session%20on%20wheat%20stalk%20painting%20was%20to%20change%20her%20life%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWheat%20stalk%20painting%2C%20a%20traditional%20art%20form%20of%20Bahraich%2C%20is%20a%20laborious%20and%20time%20consuming%20process.%20It%20is%20created%20by%20cutting%20wheat%20stalks%20into%20fine%20sections%20to%20craft%20intricate%20designs%20on%20cloth%20using%20sharp-edged%20blades%20and%20razors.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F16da3002-9bec-4787-82bb-10e845c9c0f2-1722256456.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Some%20of%20Rachna's%20beautiful%20paintings%20made%20from%20wheat%20stalk.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F16da3002-9bec-4787-82bb-10e845c9c0f2-1722256456.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F16da3002-9bec-4787-82bb-10e845c9c0f2-1722256456-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F16da3002-9bec-4787-82bb-10e845c9c0f2-1722256456-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F16da3002-9bec-4787-82bb-10e845c9c0f2-1722256456-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F16da3002-9bec-4787-82bb-10e845c9c0f2-1722256456-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358949%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESome%20of%20Rachna%E2%80%99s%20beautiful%20paintings%20made%20from%20wheat%20stalk.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20class%2010%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20study%20further%20because%20the%20government%20inter%20college%20was%20very%20far%20away%20fro