html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Wargames%20show%20the%20US%20could%20burn%20through%20its%20ammo%20in%20'as%20few%20as%203%20to%204%20weeks'%20in%20a%20war%20with%20China%2C%20commission%20warns%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222558%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Arleigh%20Burke-class%20guided-missile%20destroyer%20USS%20Fitzgerald%2C%20while%20participating%20in%20Exercise%20Rim%20of%20the%20Pacific%202024%2C%20fires%20a%20naval%20strike.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a8687dfb6d32635ee4ca5c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20new%20review%20from%20a%20congressionally%20appointed%20commission%20on%20national%20defense%20warned%20that%20the%20US%20not%20prepared%20for%20war%20against%20China%20or%20Russia%2C%20let%20alone%20both%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3Cp%3EUS%20Navy%20photo%20by%20Petty%20Officer%202nd%20Class%20Jordan%20Jennings%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20new%20formal%20review%20warned%20that%20US%20munitions%20may%20last%20only%20a%20few%20weeks%20in%20a%20war%20with%20China.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20important%20weapons%2C%20like%20anti-ship%20missiles%2C%20may%20only%20last%20a%20few%20days%2C%20the%20114-page%20report%20warned.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPublished%20by%20a%20congressionally%20appointed%20commission%2C%20the%20review%20warned%20of%20deficiencies%20across%20the%20board.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20new%20high-profile%20report%20on%20US%20national%20defense%20acknowledged%20that%20the%20Pentagon%20could%20deplete%20its%20munitions%20within%20%26quot%3Bthree%20to%20four%20weeks%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20protracted%20war%20with%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rand.org%2Fnsrd%2Fprojects%2FNDS-commission.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E114-page%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20published%20on%20Monday%20by%20a%20bipartisan%20commission%20appointed%20by%20Congress%2C%20warned%20urgently%20that%20the%20US%20is%20unprepared%20for%20a%20sustained%20conflict%20with%20China%20or%20Russia%2C%20much%20less%20both%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20its%20assessments%20were%20based%20on%20previously%20reported%20material.%20Still%2C%20the%20review%20concentrates%20a%20slew%20of%20recent%20findings%20and%20dozens%20of%20officials'%20testimonies%20into%20a%20formal%20and%20dire%20recommendation%20for%20the%20US%20to%20increase%20defense%20spending%20and%20streamline%20its%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmmunition%20stockpiles%20are%20particularly%20lacking%2C%20said%20the%20eight-person%20commission%2C%20which%20included%20a%20retired%20Army%20general%2C%20a%20former%20Democratic-party%20congresswoman%2C%20and%20a%20former%20US%20ambassador.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20cited%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnas.org%2Fpress%2Fpress-release%2Fnew-cnas-report-precision-and-posture-defense-spending-trends-and-the-fy23-budget-request%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2022%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20two%20Center%20for%20National%20American%20Security%20analysts%20that%20said%20the%20US%20doesn't%20have%20enough%20arms%20to%20%26quot%3Bblunt%20and%20defeat%20an%20initial%20invasion%26quot%3B%20from%20powers%20like%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20commissioners%20added%20that%20this%20shortage%20has%20endured%20even%20after%20the%20US%20recently%20intensified%20arms%20production%20to%20supply%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20result%2C%20unclassified%20public%20wargames%20suggest%20that%2C%20in%20a%20conflict%20with%20China%2C%20the%20United%20States%20would%20largely%20exhaust%20its%20munitions%20inventories%20in%20as%20few%20as%20three%20to%20four%20weeks%2C%26quot%3B%20their%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20important%20munitions%2C%20such%20as%20anti-ship%20missiles%2C%20could%20last%20only%20a%20few%20days%2C%20the%20commission%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20commissioners%20said%20stockpiles%20among%20US%20allies%20are%20also%20a%20concern.%20As%20an%20example%2C%20they%20cited%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.rusi.org%2F359-SR-Ukraine-Preliminary-Lessons-Feb-July-2022-web-final.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%202022%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Royal%20United%20Services%20Institute%20about%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20report%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BAt%20the%20height%20of%20the%20fighting%20in%20Donbas%2C%20Russia%20was%20using%20more%20ammunition%20in%20two%20days%20than%20the%20entire%20British%20military%20has%20in%20stock.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f91d615e-1289-47ec-a34b-3d148176d709%5C%22%3EDefense%20industry%20'grossly%20inadequate'%20even%20in%20peacetime%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20commission%20warned%20that%20defense%20production%20as%20a%20whole%20is%20in%20bad%20shape%2C%20saying%20the%20wider%20industry%20doesn't%20have%20the%20capacity%20to%20meet%20national%20needs%20even%20in%20peacetime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUS%20industrial%20production%20is%20grossly%20inadequate%20to%20provide%20the%20equipment%2C%20technology%2C%20and%20munitions%20needed%20today%2C%20let%20alone%20given%20the%20demands%20of%20great%20power%20conflict%2C%26quot%3B%20their%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20they%20warned%20of%20a%20spectrum%20of%20deficiencies%20in%20the%20US%2C%20including%20a%20need%20for%20better%20career%20incentives%20to%20recruit%20military%20personnel%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bbyzantine%26quot%3B%20research%20and%20development%20process%2C%20and%20a%20slow%2C%20bureaucratic%20Defense%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFundamental%20shifts%20in%20threats%20and%20technology%20require%20fundamental%20change%20in%20how%20DoD%20functions%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20commission%20proposed%20several%20major%20changes%20to%20the%20way%20the%20US%20plans%20defense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Ball%20elements%20of%20national%20power%26quot%3B%20strategy%20incorporating%20the%20private%20and%20civil%20sectors.%20This%20mirrors%2C%20in%20principle%2C%20what%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxi-jinping-order-military-collaborate-tech-giants-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina%20has%20been%20doing%20with%20its%20own%20defense%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20leveraging%20on%20civilian%20companies%20and%20state-run%20conglomerates%20that%20can%20work%20together%20with%20its%20military%20and%20prepare%20for%20wartime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20is%20a%20%26quot%3BMultiple%20Theater%20Force%20Construct%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20aims%20to%20address%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-no-longer-fight-two-major-wars-at-same-time-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elarge-scale%20conflicts%20against%20multiple%20world%20powers%20%3C%2Fa%3Esimultaneously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20strategy%20is%20a%20step%20up%20from%20the%20more%20traditional%20%26quot%3Btwo-war%20construct%26quot%3B%20idea%20of%20the%20US%20being%20prepared%20to%20fight%20wars%20against%20two%20regional%20threats%2C%20such%20as%20Iran%20or%20North%20Korea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20review%20further%20stressed%20that%20the%20US%20public%20is%20%26quot%3Blargely%20unaware%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20threats%20to%20their%20country%20and%20its%20allies%2C%20saying%20that%20most%20Americans%20don't%20understand%20how%20major%20war%20stands%20to%20affect%20every%20aspect%20of%20their%20lives%20%E2%80%94%20from%20water%20and%20power%20supplies%20to%20internet%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20bipartisan%20'call%20to%20arms'%20is%20urgently%20needed%20so%20that%20the%20United%20States%20can%20make%20the%20major%20changes%20and%20significant%20investments%20now%20rather%20than%20wait%20for%20the%20next%20Pearl%20Harbor%20or%209%2F11%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-run-out-ammo-weeks-ch