re%20price%20has%20cratered%20since%20then.%3Cp%3EBennett%20Raglin%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBuzzFeed%20is%20a%20digital%20publisher%20that%20used%20to%20attract%20a%20lot%20of%20attention%20from%20people%20who%20thought%20it%20was%20the%20future%20of%20media.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%2C%20it%20attracts%20people%20who%20think%20it%20is%20mismanaged%20and%20want%20to%20change%20the%20way%20CEO%20Jonah%20Peretti%20runs%20the%20company.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20it%20remains%20unclear%20how%20BuzzFeed%20investors%20can%20influence%20Peretti's%20ownership.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202021%2C%20BuzzFeed%20was%20worth%20around%20%241%20billion.%20Now%20it's%20worth%20%24100%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVarun%20Gupta%20thinks%20it%20should%20be%20worth%20more.%20Gupta%2C%20who%20runs%20a%20small%20hedge%20fund%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.prnewswire.com%2Fnews-releases%2Fedge-one-capital-takes-stake-in-buzzfeed-302207816.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esays%20he's%20acquired%20a%20stake%20in%20the%20digital%20publisher%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20has%20ideas%20for%20how%20to%20increase%20its%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20good%20news%20for%20Gupta%2C%20who%20tells%20me%20he's%20bought%20somewhere%20between%201%25%20and%205%25%20of%20BuzzFeed's%20shares%2C%20is%20that%20BuzzFeed%20CEO%20and%20founder%20Jonah%20Peretti%20also%20thinks%20the%20company%20should%20be%20worth%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bad%20news%20is%20Peretti%20seems%20uninterested%20in%20Gupta's%20suggestions%3A%20Gupta%20says%20a%20note%20he%20sent%20Peretti's%20company%20on%20July%209%20has%20not%20generated%20a%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20not%20totally%20surprising%2C%20given%20that%20Gupta's%20primary%20critique%20of%20BuzzFeed%20seems%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvivek-ramaswamy-buzzfeed-theories-why-buying-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBuzzFeed's%20capital%20structure%2C%20which%20gives%20Peretti%20voting%20control%20of%20the%20company%20even%20though%20he%20doesn't%20own%20a%20majority%20of%20its%20shares%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20we've%20noted%20here%20before%2C%20that%20kind%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmurdoch-moguls-media-tech-dual-class-stock-control-how-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edual-class%20stock%20structure%20isn't%20unique%20among%20media%20and%20tech%20companies%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20is%20meant%20to%20insulate%20BuzzFeed%20from%20demands%20from%20people%20like%20Gupta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20since%20I'm%20a%20journalist%2C%20I'm%20duty-bound%20to%20report%20that%20there%20are%20now%20three%20investors%20who%20say%20they've%20bought%20stock%20in%20BuzzFeed%20and%20want%20it%20to%20change.%20So%20it's%20a%20trend!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuzzfeed-needs-hot-ones-deal-fend-off-vivek-ramaswamy-2024-6%3Futm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dtwitter%26utm_campaign%3Dtech-sf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVivek%20Ramaswamy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20former%20Republican%20presidential%20candidate%20who%20has%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sec.gov%2FArchives%2Fedgar%2Fdata%2F1828972%2F000200799724000014%2FxslSCHEDULE_13D_X01%2Fprimary_doc.xml%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESecurities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%20he%20owns%208.9%25%20of%20BuzzFeed%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20there's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.bloomberglaw.com%2Fesg%2Fbuzzfeed-rises-after-pulte-takes-activist-stake-backs-ramaswamy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBill%20Pulte%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20describes%20himself%20as%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fpulte%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETwitter%20philanthropist%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20has%20told%20me%20he%20has%20purchased%20less%20than%201%25%20of%20BuzzFeed%2C%20and%20says%20he%20supports%20Ramaswamy's%20BuzzFeed%20plans%3B%20and%20Gupta%2C%20who%20runs%20the%20Edge%20One%20Capital%20fund%20from%20North%20Carolina.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGupta%20says%20he's%20working%20independently%20of%20Ramaswamy%20and%20that%20he%20was%20interested%20in%20BuzzFeed%20prior%20to%20Ramaswamy's%20May%2022%20announcement%20when%20he%20first%20disclosed%20his%20BuzzFeed%20stake.%20He%20says%20he's%20somewhat%20aligned%20with%20Ramaswamy's%20critique%20that%20BuzzFeed%20caters%20too%20much%20to%20the%20left%2C%20but%20is%20more%20concerned%20about%20Peretti's%20voting%20power%20and%20BuzzFeed's%20balance%20sheet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20does%2C%20however%2C%20want%20BuzzFeed%20to%20start%20running%20coverage%20of%20%26quot%3Bbipartisan%20politics%2C%20entrepreneurship%2C%20crypto%2C%20stocks%2C%20and%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20writes%20in%20his%20July%20letter%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D26f679ca8859a3d1b3579547a61b1061a4d8319820aef3eed40e81c0d22a4573%26postID%3D66a80d542ef1da46c7225839%26postSlug%3Dbuzzfeed-varun-gupta-bill-pulte-vivek-ramaswamy-jonah-peretti-2024-7%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.scribd.com%252Fdocument%252F754442540%252FBuzzFeed-Edge-One-Capital%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3BThese%20are%20topics%20with%20high%20follower%20interest%2C%20and%20by%20increasing%20content%20in%20these%20areas%2C%20BuzzFeed%20can%20greatly%20expand%20and%20enhance%20platform%20usage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20think%20there's%20much%20more%20to%20say%20about%20that%2C%20for%20the%20time%20being.%20BuzzFeed's%20fundamental%20situation%20remains%20unchanged%20since%20Ramaswamy%20disclosed%20his%20ownership%3A%20The%20company%20has%20a%20beaten-up%20share%20price%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20debt%2C%20and%20a%20setup%20that%20means%20the%20equity%20shares%20Ramaswamy%2C%20Pulte%20and%20Gupta%20own%20don't%20get%20them%20a%20seat%20at%20the%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D