along%20with%20his%20nieces%2C%20Vinesh%20and%20Priyanka%2C%20faced%20resistance%20from%20villagers%2C%20including%20his%20own%20family.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20life%20inspired%20the%20Aamir%20Khan-starrer%20Bollywood%20movie%2C%20Dangal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllowing%20the%20girls%20to%20enter%20the%20mud%20pit%2C%20traditionally%20seen%20as%20a%20male%20domain%2C%20was%20met%20with%20significant%20opposition%20in%20his%20village%20Balali%20in%20Charkhi%20Dadri%20district%20(then%20in%20Bhiwani).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20almost%20a%20year-and-a-half%20later%2C%20an%20initiative%20to%20allow%20girls%20to%20train%20alongside%20boys%20at%20Chotu%20Ram%20Stadium%20Wrestling%20Centre%20in%20Rohtak%20faced%20societal%20hurdles.%20Former%20wrestlers%2C%20and%20even%20some%20coaches%2C%20expressed%20reservations%2C%20questioning%20%E2%80%9Chow%20goats%20could%20stay%20among%20the%20lions%E2%80%9D%2C%20fearing%20that%20the%20presence%20of%20girls%20would%20distract%20boys%2C%20leading%20to%20indiscipline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFast%20forward%20to%202024.%20What%20was%20once%20met%20with%20sarcasm%E2%80%94people%20comparing%20girls%20to%20goats%20and%20boys%20to%20lions%2C%20emphasising%20the%20perceived%20disparity%20in%20strength%20and%20prowess%20in%20the%20wrestling%20arena%E2%80%94has%20now%20become%20a%20point%20of%20pride.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaryana%E2%80%99s%20women%20wrestlers%20have%20emerged%20as%20the%20flag%20bearers%20of%20Indian%20wrestling%20on%20the%20global%20stage.%20At%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fvideo%2Ffarmers-daughter-set-to-rock-paris-olympics-archery-shorts-parisolympics2024-sports%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2024%20Paris%20Olympics%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20India%20is%20represented%20by%20six%20wrestlers%2C%20five%20of%20whom%20are%20women%20from%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20rural%20landscape%2C%20where%20they%20once%20faced%20stiff%20opposition%20to%20entering%20the%20male-dominated%20sport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMeet%20the%20team%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20wrestling%20contingent%20in%20Paris%20comprises%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20(50kg)%20from%20Charkhi%20Dadri%2C%20Antim%20Panghal%20(53kg)%20from%20Hisar%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F263525%2Fanshu-malik-first-indian-woman-world-wrestling-championship-winner%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Anshu%20Malik%20(57kg)%20from%20Jind%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Nisha%20Dahiya%20(68kg)%20from%20Panipat%2C%20Reetika%20Hooda%20(76kg)%20from%20Rohtak%2C%20along%20with%20the%20lone%20male%20wrestler%2C%20Aman%20Sehrawat%20(57kg)%20from%20Jhajjar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COlympics%20is%20every%20sportsperson%E2%80%99s%20dream%2C%20and%20I%20am%20feeling%20happy%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20sporting%20event%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Reetika%20Hooda%2C%20who%20hails%20from%20Kharkara%20Village%20in%20Rohtak.%20%E2%80%9CMoreover%2C%20Indian%20women%20wrestlers%20leading%20the%20Indian%20charge%20in%20Paris%20is%20a%20great%20motivation%20for%20its%20future%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%E2%80%99s%20wrestling%20was%20introduced%20in%20the%20Olympics%20at%20the%202004%20Athens%20Games%2C%20and%20Indian%20women%20wrestlers%20made%20their%20debut%20at%20the%202012%20London%20Olympics.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20Phogat%20family%20has%20been%20represented%20in%20every%20Olympic%20Games%2C%20including%20in%20Paris%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20started%20with%20Mahavir%E2%80%99s%20eldest%20daughter%20Geeta%2C%20who%20became%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20first%20woman%20wrestler%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20Olympics%20at%20the%202012%20London%20Games.%20In%20the%20next%20edition%2C%20it%20was%20Babita%20and%20Vinesh%2C%20and%20followed%20just%20by%20Vinesh%20in%20the%202020%20Tokyo%20Olympics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202024%20Paris%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F170013%2Fwrestling-phogat-dangal-laureus-award-sports%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVinesh%20will%20be%20competing%20in%20her%20third%20Olympics%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20becoming%20the%20first%20Indian%20woman%20wrestler%20to%20feature%20in%20three%20quadrennial%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20introduced%20the%20family%20girls%20into%20wrestling%2C%20my%20aim%20was%20an%20Olympic%20medal.%20The%20girls%20have%20won%20all%20the%20medals%2C%20and%20now%20only%20the%20Olympic%20medal%20is%20missing.%20I%20hope%20Vinesh%20will%20win%20it%20this%20time%20in%20Paris%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mahavir%20Phogat%2C%20their%20mentor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20961px)%20100vw%2C%20961px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG-20240725-WA0590-1722002469.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22961%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Phogat%20sisters.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG-20240725-WA0590-1722002469.jpg%20961w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG-20240725-WA0590-1722002469-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG-20240725-WA0590-1722002469-500x666.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG-20240725-WA0590-1722002469-768x1023.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG-20240725-WA0590-1722002469-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG-20240725-WA0590-1722002469-150x200.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358785%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Phogat%20sisters.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202010%20Commonwealth%20Games%2C%20hosted%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20saw%20women%E2%80%99s%20wrestling%20making%20its%20debut%20in%20the%20Commonwealth%20Games%2C%20and%20the%20performance%20of%20the%20Indian%20women%20wrestlers%E2%80%94three%20gold%2C%20two%20silver%2C%20and%20a%20bronze%E2%80%94changed%20society%E2%80%99s%20mindset%20towards%20women%20wrestlers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20no%20longer%20recognize%20them%20as%20goats%20but%20have%20started%20seeing%20them%20as%20lionesses%20in%20the%20wrestling%20arena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20been%20a%20long%20journey%2C%20from%20villagers%20being%20up%20in%20arms%20against%20the%20move%20of%20making%20the%20girls%20slug%20it%20out%20with%20boys%20in%20the%20mud%20pit%2C%20to%20the%20entire%20village%20standing%20in%20their%20honour%20for%20the%20women%20wrestlers%20winning%20medals%20at%20the%202010%20Commonwealth%20Games.%20Since%20then%2C%20Indian%20women%20wrestlers%20have%20excelled%20on%20the%20world%20stage%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mahavir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20five%20of%20them%20making%20it%20to%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%20speaks%20a%20lot%20about%20women%20wrestling%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202016%20Rio%20Olympics%2C%20an%20edition%20after%20the%20Indian%20women%20wrestlers%20made%20their%20Olympic%20debut%2C%20a%20trainee%20of%20Rohtak%E2%80%99s%20Chotu%20Ram%20Wrestling%20Centre%2C%20Sakshi%20Malik%2C%20became%20the%20first%20Indian%20woman%20wrestler%20to%20win%20an%20Olympic%20medal.%20She%20won%20bronze%20in%20Rio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20the%20women%20trainees%20of%20the%20centre%20have%20had%20a%20presence%20in%20every%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%20Tokyo%2C%20Seema%20Bisla%2C%20who%20trained%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20at%20the%20centre%2C%20was%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20wrestling%20contingent.%20Now%2C%20in%202024%20Paris%2C%20the%20centre%20is%20represented%20through%20its%20trainee%20Reetika%20Hooda%2C%20who%20is%20the%20first%20Indian%20woman%20wrestler%20in%20the%20heavyweight%20category%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CImmediately%20after%20women%E2%80%99s%20wrestling%20was%20introduced%20in%20Haryana%2C%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20girls%20began%20making%20their%20presence%20felt%20at%20the%20national%20level%2C%20and%20gradually%20the%20Indian%20women%E2%80%99s%20wrestling%20squad%20became%20largely%20an%20all-Haryana%20affair%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Mandeep%2C%20a%20coach%20at%20the%20centre%20under%20whom%20Sakshi%20Malik%20and%20Reetika%20train.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20in%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%2C%20the%20women%20wrestlers%20from%20Haryana%20have%20become%20synonymous%20with%20Indian%20wrestling.%20It%20feels%20nice%20that%20you%20have%20contributed%20your%20bit%20to%20this%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20the%20years%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20wrestling%20has%20seen%20a%20vertical%20growth.%20A%20decade%20ago%2C%20there%20were%20around%2020%20girls%20at%20the%20Rohtak%20centre%2C%20and%20now%20the%20number%20has%20crossed%20100.%20And%20I%20am%20only%20talking%20about%20one%20training%20centre.%20Now%20there%20are%20many%20more%20such%20centres%20for%20women%20across%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20coach%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndian%20women%20wrestlers%20are%20doing%20very%20well%2C%20and%20we%20are%20expecting%20a%20couple%20of%20medals%20from%20them%20in%20Paris%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFamily%20support%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20when%20society%20was%20not%20accepting%20the%20women%20from%20the%20khap%20land%20of%20Haryana%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20wrestling%20world%2C%20it%20was%20the%20unconditional%20support%20of%20family%2C%20especially%20the%20parents%2C%20that%20kept%20women%E2%80%99s%20wrestling%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C